						<li>At a specific date time each week.</li>
					</ul><br/>
					<div class="note">
						<h4>Note</h4>
						<div>For date based reboots Cron must be activated. See <a href="HManagement.asp">Management</a> for Cron activation.</div>
					</div>
					</dd>
